      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing exceptional lateral dynamics and precise gear transitions. The variable M differential lock ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid flush and inspection of the rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure powertrain integrity. A performance-oriented build with a rigid chassis and visceral induction note, perfectly suited for the spirited driver.",
